{"tid":829532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馮檢基：不滿不設初選會考慮參選","createTime":"2018-09-20T13:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T14:27:54.000Z","uid":64345,"like":10,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a4f0d9b96c83fafda08d9167e4ea0fb59878b12d","tid":829532,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】立法會九龍西補選十一月底舉行，下月二號起接受提名。劉小麗率先宣布代表民主派參選，工黨李卓人會作後備人選，馮檢基不滿民主派不設初選，自己會考慮參選。<br />\n<br />\n因宣誓被法庭裁定無效，喪失議員資格的劉小麗在補選提名期前率先宣布會捲土重來。<br />\n<br />\n早前獲民主派通過作為後備人選的工黨李卓人一直站在劉小麗旁邊，除了議會內各黨派的代表出席支持，在九龍西有多名區議員的民協亦都有代表到場。已退出民協的馮檢基表明，一旦劉小麗被取消參選資格，自己會考慮參選。劉小麗不願評估對民主派勝算的影響。<br />\n<br />\n在上次泛民初選中落敗說過是自己最後一戰的馮檢基批評，民主派今次不設初選，不排除自己復出參選。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=320995\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D320995&d=nD3x63jW2otb9wdOfdZtFzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=244fab52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D320995&h=a46592bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=320995</a><br />\n<br />\n𠝹票王"},{"pid":"bf39e85e29e008375d781eb6751265d234509fcb","tid":829532,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"又黎幫民建聯助攻"},{"pid":"54486836480eeff0f47eb4f31570a825880319ba","tid":829532,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T13:45:07.000Z","msg":"又黎..."},{"pid":"93957b3fe8866a4c6fddde3a70facac6e259989c","tid":829532,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T13:47:38.000Z","msg":"馮檢基︰九西不能少了我 / 没有我，泛民不會完整 / 我是泛民中的關鍵"},{"pid":"1a78dda8726b8eb96555938f7a62cc6c7f8ed9b6","tid":829532,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T13:47:42.000Z","msg":"後備都無份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ad14a086129572f